Name: Indoor Rock Climbing VR
About the game: Indoor Rock Climbing VR is a hands-on climbing enthusiasts dream. Designed specifically for Virtual Reality, you are able to climb up short to tall sets, jump from handle to handle, and navigate a horizontal-climbing arena. Move with ease and grab handles one-by-one with controllers. Appropriate for both simulation-seekers and casual gamers. Music Included! SteamVR and Oculus support.
